text: Windemere may refer to: * Windemere Township, Minnesota * Windemere, North Carolina, a census designated place (CDP) * Windemere, Texas, a CDP * Windemere (Walloon Lake), the Hemingway home on Walloon Lake in northern Michigan, listed on the National Register of Historic Places ==See also== * Windermere (disambiguation) * Windamere (disambiguation)
title: Windemere
